	<feedback mode="101" id="1">
		<paragraph x="0" y="+0" width="407" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000">11. The speaker says that if you overload the site with too much text it can look very unattractive so she does not think this is a good design feature.</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
